   Alcohol Alert
   A quarterly bulletin that disseminates important research findings on a
   single aspect of alcohol abuse and alcoholism

   Alcohol Research & Health
   NIAAA's quarterly, peer-reviewed scientific journal (formerly Alcohol
   Health & Research World)
   Alcohol Research: Achievements and Promise
    The American Journal on Addictions, Volume 10, Number 1 Supplement
   2001
     (Presented with permission from the @2001 American Academy of
   Addiction Psychiatry)

   Congressional Report
   A triennial report containing authoritative reviews of current research
   on alcohol abuse and alcoholism, 10th Special Report to the U.S.
   Congress on Alcohol & Health [PDF] [viewing info/online ordering]

   Epidemiologic Manuals/Directories
   Data directories and manuals on alcohol-related problems

   Pamphlets/Brochures
   Easy-to-read material for the public covering a wide range of
   alcohol-related topics including Publicaciones en Espa√±ol
   Reports/Manuals/Guides
   Treatment, prevention and training materials for health care providers
   and researchers

   Thesaurus
   A comprehensive resource of more than 10,000 alcohol and other drug
   terms including a subset index of language used in the Alcohol Problems
   Science Database (commonly known as ETOH)

